Module PA2
Package model

Class GameLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.GameLevel
  • public class GameLevel
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that loads, stores, modifies, and keeps track of the game map win/deadlock condition. Also keeps tracks of information about this current level, e.g. how many moves the player has made.
